{"serial": "52050", "department_serial": 51, "code": "CE6154", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "System Component Design for Emerging Memory and Storage Technologies", "ch": "新興記憶儲存系統元件設計"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen Tseng-Yi"], "ch": ["陳增益"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "E6", "room": "A205"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 40, "department": {"ch": "資訊工程學系", "en": "Department of Computer Science and Elec. Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 23, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程目的主要介紹應用在新興記憶儲存架構的記憶與儲存技術(例如：非揮發性記憶體、開放通道快閃記憶體、疊瓦式硬碟)。接著探討目前作業系統中記憶體管理、快取管理與儲存系統管理在這些新興記憶儲存架構中的存取管理方法設計與傳統設計遭遇到的設計挑戰。", "en": "“The objective of this course is to introduce emerging memory and storage technologies (i.e., non-volatile memory, open-channel solid-state drives, and shingled magnetic recording drives). Furthermore, this course will discuss how data management units (e.g., cache, memory, and storage system components) in a modern operating system deal with file access operations and storage space management over these emerging memory and storage devices. Based on the discussions, students should have ability to find challenges and difficulties in emerging memory storage system designs.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "“本課程分為六個授課單元\n1. 作業系統內快取、記憶體與檔案系統介紹\n2. 區塊式儲存裝置介紹\n3. 嵌入式儲存系統架構\n4. 非揮發性記憶體技術與管理系統\n5. 混合式儲存裝置與虛擬化儲存系統\n6. 最新記憶儲存系統研究探討“", "en": "“This course is composed of six major parts:\n1. Cache, memory, and storage management in an operating system.\n2. Block-based storage device introduction\n3. Embedded memory and storage architecture\n4. Non-volatile memory technology and its management designs.\n5. Hybrid storage device and storage virtualization\n6. The research discussions on the latest memory and storage systems.“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "參考書：Information Storage and Management", "en": "Reference book: Information Storage and Management"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "85", "en": "85"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“課堂參與成績 (10％)\n作業報告 (20％)\n期中報告 (30％)\n期末專題 (40％)“", "en": "“Attendance (10％)\nAssignment (20％)\nMidterm Report (30％)\nFinal Project (40％)“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三15:00-16:00、星期四11:00-12:00", "en": "Wednesday 15:00-16:00 and Thursday 11:00-12:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "專題實作與展示", "en": "專題實作與展示"}, "domain": {"ch": "資安、網路、資料庫與系統研究群", "en": "資安、網路、資料庫與系統研究群"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "發掘、分析及處理問題的能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "資訊工程專業知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "組織表達能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "創新及獨立思考之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "溝通協調與團隊合作能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "洞察資訊技術潮流與國際趨勢", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "專案規畫與管理之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "終身學習與自我成長之能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Problem Discovery and Solving", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Information Technology Expertise", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "Organization and Presentation", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research